content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 195.17 - Statement of licensure

State Regulations

All documents or receipts issued by an individual or
business licensed pursuant to this article must contain the identification
number issued to such individual or business and the phrase "licensed by the
N.Y.S. Department of State."
